thread.title: BRIEF-Ayima San Francisco Office Signs New Client Contract

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Ayima San Francisco Office Signs New Client Contract

organizations.name: brief-ayima san francisco office signs new client

text:
March 7 (Reuters) - AYIMA GROUP AB (PUBL):
* AYIMA SAN FRANCISCO OFFICE SIGNS MAJOR NEW CLIENT CONTRACT
* NEW ENGAGEMENT WILL COMMENCE DURING MARCH 2018 AND BEGIN TO BE FULLY REFLECTED IN Q2, 2018 RESULTS
* VALUE OF CONTRACT WILL BE A MINIMUM OF APPROXIMATELY 2 MSEK IN FIRST YEAR (AT CURRENT EXCHANGE RATES)
* NEW ENGAGEMENT IS FOR SEARCH ENGINE OPTIMISATION (SEO) SERVICE AND
* CONSISTS OF A LONG-TERM RETAINER AGREEMENT FOR A MINIMUM OF 12 MONTHS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
